1. *Čula* je stigla do mene preko vijesti na televiziji. (The news reached me through the television.)
2. On je odlučio da se odmah *čula* sa mojim otacom. (He decided to talk to my father immediately.)
3. Svi smo se čudili kada smo *čula* da je on iznenada otišao. (We were all surprised when we heard that he had suddenly left.)
4. *Čula* je da će biti velika poplava u sledećem mesecu. (It was heard that there will be a big flood next month.)
5. Ova pjesma je često *čula* na radiju. (This song is often heard on the radio.)